::KitKat::

Once she saw that all the bots were on board, she hit the thrusters 
into over drive and lifted the pod off the ground. She took off, 
heading for the new base. "Hold onto something, it could get bumpy."

She wasn't used to flying a pod. She had never flown one before. She 
had read the manual and the rest was guess work. But she wasn't going 
to tell anyone that.
